<div class="hottest">
  <div class="dx-wrapper">
    <div class="pull-left" style="width: 700px; margin-right: 30px;">
      <div style="margin-top: 40px;">
        <h1 style="margin-bottom: 30px;">Bring people who share your dream</h1>
        <p style="font-size: 20px; margin-bottom: 30px;">Curious how it works?</p>
        <button style="font-size: 22px; margin-bottom: 40px;">了解更多</button>
      </div>
      <div>
        程序员在2个人的支持下，筹集2000元买了999朵玫瑰送给心仪的女孩，十动然拒。
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="pull-left">
      <%= image_tag 'project-sample.png' %>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix">
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="dx-wrapper">
  <div class="recommand">
    <div class="project pull-left">
      <h2>编辑推荐：微电影</h2>
      <div class="video pull-left">
        <iframe height=298 width=310 src="http://player.youku.com/embed/XMzk1NjM4MzMy" frameborder=0 allowfullscreen></iframe>
      </div>
      <div class="detail pull-left">
        <div class="title">
          咸蛋超人大战肉蒲团
        </div>
        <div class="meta">
          by 韦索楠 in 广州,广东
        </div>
        <div class="description">
          这是一部不存在的电影，表示只是单纯的为了撑下场面，填个description什么的。说起来description写个什么好呢？网站连名字都没有是个蛋。
        </div>
        <div class="progress">
          94% 达到 | 已筹$3,600 | 还剩6天
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="category pull-left">
      <ul>
        <% %w(电影 慈善 体育 科技 设计).each do |c| %>
          <li><a><%= c %></a></li>
        <% end %>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="clearfix"></div>
  </div>
  <div class="projects">
    <div class="region" style="font-size: 22px;">
      广州，广东
    </div>
    <% @projects.each do |project| %>
      <div class="project-item">
        <div class="title"><%= link_to (project.try(:basic_info).try(:name) || "(项目未命名)"), project_path(project) %></div>
        <div class="creator"><%= "By #{project.try(:user).try(:name)}" if project.user %></div>
        <div class="description"><%= project.try(:story).try(:introduction) || "(未有描述)" %></div>
      </div>
    <% end %>
    <% (4 - @projects.count).times do |i| %>
      <div class="project-item">
        <div class="title"><%= "项目#{i}" %></div>
        <div class="creator"><%= "用户#{i}" %></div>
        <div class="description"><%= "(未有描述)" %></div>
      </div>
    <% end %>

  </div>

<div class="clearfix"></div>

